# =============================================================================
# .gitignore — FarmLink
# Actualizado en Fase 0 (saneamiento): se consolidaron duplicados y se agregaron
# exclusiones esenciales que faltaban (node_modules, .env, dist, etc.)
# =============================================================================

# --- Dependencias ---
node_modules/
.pub-cache/
.dart_tool/

# --- Variables de entorno (NUNCA versionar secretos) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Compilados y builds ---
dist/
build/
coverage/

# --- Logs ---
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*

# --- macOS ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*._.DS_Store
__MACOSX/

# --- IDEs ---
.idea/
.vscode/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln

# --- Claude Code (herramienta de desarrollo local) ---
.claude/

# --- Flutter específico ---
*.g.dart
*.freezed.dart

# --- Fases y planificación (Claude / desarrollo interno) ---
fases/
Fases/
prompts/
*.prompt.md
PLAN_DE_TRABAJO_LOCAL.md

# --- Builds específicos ---
Backend/dist/
frontend-react/node_modules/
frontend-react/dist/